  "id": "RAW_cb947b1c",
  "title": "2025 我们这样用 Kimi Agent 新技能，你也可以",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0NDU1MDkyNg==&mid=2247487857&idx=1&sn=52e7a59cb291f1633b61a2ebb82fabdd",
  "date": "2025-12-22 13:03:00",
  "author": "月之暗面 Kimi",
  "siteName": "月之暗面 Kimi",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <blockquote class=\"js_blockquote_wrap\">\n   <div class=\"js_blockquote_digest\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-style: italic;\">Man is the most intelligent of animals because he has hands.</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"blockquote_info js_blockquote_source\" data-json=\"%7B%22type%22%3A%22out%22%2C%22article%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22from%22%3A%22Anaxagoras%22%7D\"><span class=\"blockquote_other\">Anaxagoras</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.kimi.com/\" imgurl=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXHVRia80kficCIA5tMeRtXtMQgIHPaUACJWtAPqDXS04pnH36uPNhVPhibrU7n9iarkMXUCaI2MRmacg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"outerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span style=\"width:100%;\" class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004197\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42506350550381033\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2362\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXHVRia80kficCIA5tMeRtXtMQgIHPaUACJWtAPqDXS04pnH36uPNhVPhibrU7n9iarkMXUCaI2MRmacg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"245\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fab63fd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXHVRia80kficCIA5tMeRtXtMQgIHPaUACJWtAPqDXS04pnH36uPNhVPhibrU7n9iarkMXUCaI2MRmacg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></a></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">又快到了岁末年初的交汇点，回顾 2025 年，如果只能用一个短语来形容 AI 行业的变革，那一定是：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">从「对话」走向「行动」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">其实，比起一段精彩的对话，用户更需要的始终是一个能帮忙解决实际问题的伙伴。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去一年，我们开发了擅长写代码和使用工具的 Kimi K2 和 Kimi K2 Thinking 模型，Cursor、</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNzY4NDEzNA==&amp;mid=2247484111&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=a1a1ef4d8ebefc80376c6d9352d24768&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Vercel\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Vercel</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNzY4NDEzNA==&amp;mid=2247484127&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cd795f18b263b453809c04d4b9ac6394&amp;chksm=c3654ac4a1fd86393c7a067fc17fd3a017969d3a6a362cbd75bcb612824efad281426132e5c0&amp;scene=21&amp;sessionid=1766399603&amp;subscene=227&amp;clicktime=1766399643&amp;enterid=1766399643#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Genspark\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Genspark</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzk0NDU1MDkyNg==&amp;mid=2247487638&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=00855bffd3d3b8be1aeb3dcc64caa49d&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"Perplexity\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Perplexity</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">等全球顶尖代码、Agent、搜索应用第一时间接入 API。作为模型的「第一方」使用者，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也花了很多精力把 Kimi K2 系列模型的「动手」能力发挥出来，让 Kimi 不再仅仅回答「是什么」和「为什么」，而是开始知道应该「怎么做」，并且真的尝试去做，去交付「结果」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">过去「我们问，AI答」，在对话中完成交互。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">现在，我们下指令，AI 自主去做规划，一步一步干活，直接交付结果。一场关于我们如何与 AI 一起工作的变化悄然发生：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 0px 8px 24px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">深度研究</span></span>\n   <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">曾经需要查阅数十份研报、耗费数小时的行业调研、公司调研，现在 Kimi 可以自主检索、交叉验证，并在半小时内交付一份结构严谨、内容扎实的研究报告。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100004206\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5614583333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"3840\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmecoa.qpic.cn/sz_mmecoa_png/NYNAL7XfyJXO1QND2hibuzayC6qHsmXFB0bbWNUVGLxuZvs30QHcyXTNMaZbLMTts42sOLs5lbGq9ia0k7TNENmg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"556\" data-cropsely2=\"313\" data-backw=\"556\" data-backh=\"312\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=86e87f5c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmecoa.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmecoa_png%2FNYNAL7XfyJXO1QND2hibuzayC6qHsmXFB0bbWNUVGLxuZvs30QHcyXTNMaZbLMTts42sOLs5lbGq9ia0k7TNENmg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-trans