ple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \\&quot;Noto Sans\\&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Source Han Sans SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">🔬&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;4 3 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \\&quot;Noto Sans\\&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Source Han Sans SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: bold;\">Kimi API 业务同学日常用「深度研究」做行业调研 ↑</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;4 3 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: -apple-system, \\&quot;system-ui\\&quot;, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, \\&quot;Segoe UI\\&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \\&quot;Noto Sans\\&quot;, sans-serif, Arial, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Source Han Sans SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, \\&quot;Noto Sans CJK SC\\&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: pre-wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;float: none;display: inline !important;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: bold;\">提示词：</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;font-weight: normal;\">做一份关于anthropic和aws之间合作的深度研究和分析，包括合作的商务模式、技术模式、资本模式等多方面进行分析。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 20px;font-weight: bold;\">OKC 创意实现</span></span>\n    <p style=\"margin-top: 24px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">无论是设计一个功能丰富的响应式网站原型，还是策划一场有趣的营销活动，OK Computer（简称OKC）正在从「建议者」变为「执行者」。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><